These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water, juice, mirinda
There 4 different types of food: grapes, pineapple, blueberry, cherry
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, drawing, reading, gardening
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, classical, rock, folk
4 different pets are kept: snake, fish, rabbit, ferret
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, ice-hockey, soccer, skiing
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, scooter, taxi, tram
 1. the person eating grapes is between the person drinking iced-tea and the owner of the snake##2
 2. the person eating blueberry is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
 4. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 5. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 6. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 7. the fan of classical is between the person driving the scooter and the owner of the ferret##2
 8. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 9. the person eating cherry is the fan of gospel##1
10. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person eating pineapple##1
11. the person who's sport is skiing is the person who's hobby is reading##1
12. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
13. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
14. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
15. the fan of rock is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | juice        | mirinda     | water | iced-tea      |
| Food          | blueberry | pineapple    | grapes      | cherry  |
| Hobby         | drawing  | gardening    | baking       | reading     |
| Music-Genre   | rock        | folk       | classical          | gospel |
| Pet           | rabbit    | snake | fish      | ferret     |
| Sport         | surfing   | ice-hockey   | soccer      | skiing    |
| Transport     | motorbike        | scooter        | tram    | taxi    |

