 4. the person who's sport is basketball is the owner of the hamster##1
 5. the person watching comedy movies is the person eating avocado##1
 6. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 8. the person eating cabbage is the person driving the car##1
 9. the person driving the taxi is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
10. the person eating corn is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
12. the person eating corn is between the person driving the skateboard and the person eating cauliflower##2
13. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
14. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
15. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person eating avocado##1

